message.content:
Ndiya kuthetha ngokuxhasa iintsuku zentlalo. Le nto iyakuncedisa ukuba ula kwaye ukhuthaze intetho enentiyo nenogonyamelo. 

1. Tshintsha iakhawunti yakho:
   - Hamba kwi-akhawunti yakho yabasebenzisi yakho ngeyurephu.
   - Hlela kwi-settings ngezantsi kwekhompyutha yakho.
   - Funa umthetho othile othi "Tshintsha Iakhawunti".
   - Beka iindawo ezihlukileyo ezithile ku-akhawunti yakho, ngokuthi ufuna ukugcina yeyona nto, njengengamazwi akho aphenduleyo, amazwe aphenduleyo, noma umzila aphenduleyo.
   - Beka iindlela ezihlukileyo zokukhuthaza akaunti yakho, njengokungakhathali ukuba usuka kwi-akhawunti yakho yabasebenzisi, umthetho aphenduleyo, noma iinkqubo ezihlukileyo zokutshintsha i-akhawunti.
   - Beka iindlela ezihlukileyo zokwenza umthetho, njengokubeka isithombe aphenduleyo, ukukhangela kwamavidiyo noma ukubaluleka kwemfundi aphenduleyo.

2. Hlela iinkqubo zentlalo:
   - Hamba kwi-akhawunti yakho yabasebenzisi yakho ngeyurephu.
   - Hlela kwi-settings ngezantsi kwekhompyutha yakho.
   - Funa umthetho othi "Iinkqubo zentlalo".
   - Beka iindawo ezihlukileyo ezithile ku-akhawunti yakho, njengokunyathela izikhala aphenduleyo, ukunyathela iintetho aphenduleyo, noma
